data.description: This beautiful ranch home is tucked away in the desirable Castle Pines North neighborhood. Upon entering the property, you will be greeted by an impressive foyer that leads to the spacious and new open-concept main living area. The living room is abundant in natural light from the large windows, creating a warm and welcoming ambiance. The kitchen features granite countertops, updated cabinetry, and stainless steel appliances. The adjoining dining area is perfect for entertaining guests and enjoying family meals. The home boasts a desirable layout with a generously sized bedrooms. The primary bedroom includes an ensuite bathroom complete with dual sinks,  dual showers, clawfoot tub, and vaulted ceiling. The home's finished basement includes two additional bedrooms, bathroom, entertainment room, office and spacious recreational area. Outside, the property backs to open space and is perfect for  entertaining. This home is ideally situated within close proximity to parks, shopping centers, restaurants, the Ridge golf course, Daniels Gate Park, and much more!
